title: Facebook Moves To Better Vet Ad Buyers Ahead Of 2020 Election
text: Facebook, Inc. (NASDAQ: FB) is moving to more tightly control political ads on its site as it faces a 2020 election cycle under heavy scrutiny, hoping to avoid the blame some put on the social media company for enabling interference in the 2016 presidential contest.
